 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本大部人用現金唔用電子支付添呀"},{"pid":"f11e055bc733666bdb1766d69142e7bbfc822a46","tid":431673,"uid":67771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本大把ポイントカード都係用電話掃code啦...<br />\n咁姐係話埋日本落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本成日用現金, 都唔算落後"},{"pid":"c61a027a28aa6a3b99c41ac9decb1de0c17f2ab1","tid":431673,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"我今朝上支那寶個網睇<br />\n<br />\n比呢幅圖公司D同事睇, <br />\n<br />\n成TEAM人笑到收唔到聲"},{"pid":"657edf86d4dc622bbc50dea65c91e0987d5b8f90","tid":431673,"uid":145194,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"支那寶同八達通完全冇得比，八達通一嘟就攪𠶧，支那寶仲要比個撚頭收銀嘟部手機，等佢出單先比完錢，慢八達通勁多<br />\n利伸：我自己就係個撚頭收銀，所以先知流程，自己絕對冇用過支那寶"},{"pid":"0e7df284637f10cb56ba7feda60837dfff65b219","tid":431673,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那寶同八達通完全冇得比，八達通一嘟就攪𠶧，支那寶仲要比個撚頭收銀嘟部手機，等佢出單先比完錢，慢八達通勁多<br />\n利伸：我自己就係個撚頭收銀，所以先知流程，自己絕對冇用過支那寶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以零售商戶想做多D生意, 一定要選夠快既交易方法<br />\n<br />\n否則D街客望見收銀大排長龍, 連入都唔想入去"},{"pid":"dc6709c786e66efbe76e3c600e2f2dccd6383397","tid":431673,"uid":35031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本大把ポイントカード都係用電話掃code啦...<br />\n咁姐係話埋日本落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本成日用現金, 都唔算落後</blockquote><br />\n真係低鬼能。。。日本人自己用現金用個system根本無關係<br />\n日本90％商鋪都一定用到信用卡俾錢<br />\n亦好多支援apple pay （係冇android pay姐）<br />\n電子貨幣種類多到你數唔哂 楽天edy waon 果d&hellip;<br />\n仲有日本人成日用現金係因為老一輩唔識用電子產品姐&hellip;<br />\n係東京既後生仔根本9成都係mobile suica或者quicpay俾錢&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n當然point卡都係掃code啦<br />\n一部手機搞掂哂買野、搭車、儲分&hellip;睇唔出有咩唔先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337fd39a19f186f407dc67a1ad5e16877b4ac98e","tid":431673,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那寶同八達通完全冇得比，八達通一嘟就攪𠶧，支那寶仲要比個撚頭收銀嘟部手機，等佢出單先比完錢，慢八達通勁多<br />\n利伸：我自己就係個撚頭收銀，所以先知流程，自己絕對冇用過支那寶</blockquote><br />\n我去買野就係俾個老野阻住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1751c1801ab09f5a2a42591d437d9b9ef2c1ded","tid":431673,"uid":113494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"有幾多人覺得電子支付=支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八達通公司肯去發展一下佢個技術普及到小商舖都用到唔好咩<br />\n小商舖可以用電話而唔洗裝部機收錢已經好方便啦"},{"pid":"df3e93d91c99eae9cff739eadc2f3672157a0b12","tid":431673,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登多左好多支那寶廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好出奇咩<br />\n垃圾連狗"},{"pid":"040ba23b5e9e36c7399b099a453c8f8abfff45ff","tid":431673,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾多人覺得電子支付=支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八達通公司肯去發展一下佢個技術普及到小商舖都用到唔好咩<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">小商舖可以用電話而唔洗裝部機收錢已經好方便啦</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個科技不嬲都有架, 有左好耐<br />\n<br />\n但你都要買/租個DEVICE, 因為安全交易就係加密同認證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gigaom.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/1/2011/12/izettle1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgigaom.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F1%2F2011%2F12%2Fizettle1.jpg&h=2983bb62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42cd6e46a88b39e6fb6e4103c898f605aaa6f2a5","tid":431673,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:07:59.000Z","msg":"支那寶打手竟然話帶部手機可以輕過八達通<br />\n<br />\n智力都係有問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/26niy9q20f/Mini_Octopus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F26niy9q20f%2FMini_Octopus.jpg&h=9db016bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5cb80be5294214d9fc9c540ceaf9af52f0106d6","tid":431673,"uid":2707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"不嬲要靠個app先畀到錢都係弱鳩智<br />\n不過盲反撚都唔好屌鳩晒啲電子交易再鳩捧八達通<br />\n其實睇下apple pay就知乜嘢係好嘅電子交易"},{"pid":"9694276901c278f9485afb5e6f9157e77809f9f1","tid":431673,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾多人覺得電子支付=支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八達通公司肯去發展一下佢個技術普及到小商舖都用到唔好咩<br />\n小商舖可以用電話而唔洗裝部機收錢已經好方便啦</blockquote><br />\n你以為小舖唔用八達通係因為普及唔到？"},{"pid":"ee8b1f34821543be65a604553fd5a689f5cf7e98","tid":431673,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"交上網呀??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8857ea556af7ffbc926e9ec86544905f3012a1c8","tid":431673,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"其實關個電話乜事，可唔可以 print 定張 code比人掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52a07ef3c969e02a64cc6768d146d53991f5798","tid":431673,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>QR code 其實都係石器時化產物<br />\n又唔安全，又易改又易偷<br />\n但因為成本低，支那人竟然拎來做「支付」認證。。。</blockquote><br />\n最記得以往qr code係得日本先用<br />\n最初有印象知道呢樣嘢應該係因為nike啲av會包埋張qr嘅圖之類(唔知有冇記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"bc91d2c3165c33c18fb2062e35920d116ba02a52","tid":431673,"uid":2707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本大把ポイントカード都係用電話掃code啦...<br />\n咁姐係話埋日本落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇情況啦<br />\n做人就唔使咁極端嘅<br />\nqr code唔係冇佢嘅價值，但就應該唔係用喺電子交易上面<br />\n本身啲鋪頭嘅八達通/信用卡機都有晒nfc技術啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40f41ca374c67be976071a8de3caf47345b0572","tid":431673,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實關個電話乜事，可唔可以 print 定張 code比人掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://shmrenzhen.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/9189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshmrenzhen.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2F9189.jpg&h=80cca61b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那寶一係就將自己部機個鏡頭變scanner掃code<br />\n<br />\n一係就自己個MON顯示個CODE比人掃<br />\n<br />\n玩黎玩去, 都係上個世紀既掃CODE<br />\n<br />\nAPPLE PAY先係真電子交易"},{"pid":"750f503b69bc88b0a6ef9b4075e1dad61865b1a5","tid":431673,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實關個電話乜事，可唔可以 print 定張 code比人掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個code唔變咪得<br />\n但係之前睇過電子支付post話唔知支那寶定微信玩即時generate code, 次次都要開app俾人掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e2382ba37064a03a9343ea541bf4834eb4ed30","tid":431673,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"其實都好撚危險<br />\n<br />\n有人COPY左自己個CODE個圖, 係咪可以狂掃？<br />\n<br />\n有無人解釋一下？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://video.nextmag.com.tw/photo/2015/12/09/_HAN0799_1449654264395_442419_ver1.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.nextmag.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2015%2F12%2F09%2F_HAN0799_1449654264395_442419_ver1.0.jpg&h=8878ad5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f6c4baee2d18bdf1a793bf5621c7bd78a7fefc4","tid":431673,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"唔係部部機都有nfc<br />\nqr code收錢可以唔洗申請，<br />\n街邊無牌小販都可以用黎收錢"},{"pid":"32e8eaaed20d3da0d889da517a105523421483f3","tid":431673,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實關個電話乜事，可唔可以 print 定張 code比人掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個code唔變咪得<br />\n但係之前睇過電子支付post話唔知支那寶定微信玩即時generate code, 次次都要開app俾人掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔即時generate code, 比人COPY左一次, 係咪以後可以狂掃？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321e3f00c4b1d0e4b5eb5b5e75376995f6919fc3","tid":431673,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都好撚危險<br />\n<br />\n有人COPY左自己個CODE個圖, 係咪可以狂掃？<br />\n<br />\n有無人解釋一下？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://video.nextmag.com.tw/photo/2015/12/09/_HAN0799_1449654264395_442419_ver1.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.nextmag.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2015%2F12%2F09%2F_HAN0799_1449654264395_442419_ver1.0.jpg&h=8878ad5a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n個code唔知30秒定一分鐘會轉"},{"pid":"9c53a6652d2b06b379a43e6237cb74ae69f34009","tid":431673,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係部部機都有nfc<br />\nqr code收錢可以唔洗申請，<br />\n街邊無牌小販都可以用黎收錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無牌小販隨時走鬼<br />\n<br />\n仲等你慢慢掃CODE?<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係香港住架? 有無見過香港D無牌小販?"},{"pid":"296cc03a50b82daae07483cd0c437045ca56db78","tid":431673,"uid":24023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:27:48.000Z","msg